FileSystem_FATFS_RTOS_FATFS003 App

File Structure

Following files are generated :

  1. ff.c:This is the third party source file containing all the function definations of FAT FS App.
  2. FATFS003_Conf.c: This file defines the App's Init function.
  3. FATFS003.h: This file contains function prototype & data structure declarations.
  4. ff.h: This is the third party file containing FatFs configurations and declarations
  5. ffconf.h: This is the FAT file system module configuration file.
  6. syscall.c: This contains code of OS dependent controls for FatFs.
